gengine.gameobject

Class Collectable

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.Observable
      • gengine.gameobject.GameObject
        • gengine.gameobject.Collectable

  • public class Collectable
extends GameObject
    This is the base class for collectable objects. It has value which represents the score points at this point, and enumerator Type for its type. Current types are: SCORE, POWERUP, ITEM and NONE.
    Version:
    0.2
    Author:
    Lauri Pirttimaki
